** [[citrona]] (''Citrus limon'')
** [[citronatowa citrona]] (''Citrus medica'')
** [[grapefruit]] (''Citrus x paradisi'')
** [[limeta]] (''Citrus aurantifolia'')
** [[mandarina]] (''Citrus reticulata'')
** [[pampelmuza]] (''Citrus grandis'')
** [[pomeranca]] (''Citrus aurantium'')
** [[tangelo]] (''Citrus x tangelo'')
* [[:hsb:drěwda]] (''Dictamnus'')
** [[:hsb:běła drěwda]] (''Dictamnus albus'')
